verses.text: The LORD reigneth, he is clothed with majesty; the LORD is clothed with strength, with whichhe hath girded himself: the world also is established, that it cannot be moved.
Thy throne isestablished of old: thou artfrom everlasting.
The floods have lifted up, O LORD, the floods have lifted up their voice; the floods lift their waves.
The LORD on high ismightier than the noise of many waters, yes, thanthe mighty waves of the sea.
Thy testimonies are very sure: holiness becometh thy house, O LORD, for ever.
